## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## Frontend env reference.
##
## For local dev: copy this file to .env.development.local
##   cp .env.example .env.development.local
##
## .env.development.local is git-ignored and only loaded during `npm run dev`.
## See docs/env-config.md for the full env file layout.
## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

## Cloudflare Turnstile site key (public).
# Test key below always passes — use for local dev only.
VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=1x00000000000000000000AA

## Mock mode: skip real API calls for clone/generate/design.
## Set to "true" to iterate on UI without the API Worker running.
# VITE_MOCK_CLONE=true

## API backend proxy target used by Vite `/api` proxy.
# Local default is the Cloudflare API Worker on port 8787.
BACKEND_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:8787
